WEBVTT

00:00:23.415 --> 00:00:25.834
Previously on Dating Alys Perez.

00:00:26.251 --> 00:00:27.294
Drake!

00:00:29.546 --> 00:00:31.006
Hi, girlfriend!

00:00:31.339 --> 00:00:32.883
Drake's in town.

00:00:33.550 --> 00:00:36.261
So? What are our plans tomorrow?

00:00:36.636 --> 00:00:38.513
Don't you have your classes tomorrow?

00:00:39.473 --> 00:00:40.348
Uh, no!

00:00:42.434 --> 00:00:43.894
See you tomorrow!

00:00:43.894 --> 00:00:45.103
Alys is failing, Drake.

00:00:45.103 --> 00:00:46.855
What the fuck you want, Tripp?!

00:00:47.064 --> 00:00:49.066
I'm so sorry.

00:00:49.066 --> 00:00:51.234
Mr. Scott, I'll do better.

00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:54.029
Am I really pulling you down, Alys?

00:01:06.458 --> 00:01:07.876
What did you say, Drake?

00:01:08.668 --> 00:01:10.128
I said you look different.

00:01:11.499 --> 00:01:13.459
I'll take that as a compliment.

00:01:14.714 --> 00:01:15.924
I have a question.

00:01:19.387 --> 00:01:21.973
Is it really true that
you're dating my cousin?

00:01:25.227 --> 00:01:28.230
Alys, are you dating my cousin?

00:01:28.313 --> 00:01:29.564
Yes.

00:01:30.941 --> 00:01:32.859
And what's the matter with that?

00:01:32.859 --> 00:01:33.944
Nothing.

00:01:36.238 --> 00:01:37.739
I’m just checking the competition.

00:01:39.783 --> 00:01:40.784
What?

00:01:41.993 --> 00:01:44.329
Someone told me
that since I let you go,

00:01:44.579 --> 00:01:46.373
I should be the one taking you back.

00:01:48.250 --> 00:01:49.013
Drake,

00:01:49.543 --> 00:01:50.877
Tripp is my boyfriend.

00:01:51.104 --> 00:01:52.313
What's wrong with you?

00:01:53.839 --> 00:01:55.048
But where is he?

00:01:56.633 --> 00:01:57.843
He’s in New York.

00:01:58.510 --> 00:01:59.261
And I’m here.

00:01:59.678 --> 00:02:01.429
And you’re about to get married.

00:02:18.238 --> 00:02:19.990
Hello, Baby Dane!

00:02:19.990 --> 00:02:21.324
What's up?

00:02:23.910 --> 00:02:25.871
Your weird boyfriend called me.

00:02:26.371 --> 00:02:29.583
Why would my Drakey Baby call you?

00:02:30.375 --> 00:02:32.252
Because he’s weird.

00:02:32.961 --> 00:02:33.879
What?

00:02:33.879 --> 00:02:35.755
Really? What did he say?

00:02:36.339 --> 00:02:37.924
He was just checking in.

00:02:38.466 --> 00:02:39.384
That's it?

00:02:40.010 --> 00:02:41.516
And he has updates about you.

00:02:42.071 --> 00:02:44.239
He says you're flunking your classes.

00:02:44.632 --> 00:02:45.717
What?!

00:02:45.891 --> 00:02:47.392
Drake said that?

00:02:48.226 --> 00:02:49.936
Do Mom and Dad know?

00:02:50.562 --> 00:02:52.105
I could tell them.

00:02:52.647 --> 00:02:55.734
No, Baby Dane!
Don't tell Mom and Dad!

00:02:55.734 --> 00:02:58.028
I'll get you anything you want!

00:02:58.028 --> 00:03:01.573
Just don't tell Mom and Dad
about Drake’s updates, please?

00:03:02.601 --> 00:03:03.658
Hmm...

00:03:04.492 --> 00:03:05.243
Okay.

00:03:05.911 --> 00:03:06.828
Promise?

00:03:07.495 --> 00:03:09.080
<i>Thanks, Dane!</i>
<i>Bye, bye!</i>

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:10.165
Bye, bye.

00:03:13.585 --> 00:03:14.753
I’m in trouble.

00:03:16.379 --> 00:03:18.840
I need to do better
on the exam tomorrow.

00:03:23.803 --> 00:03:25.388
Ugh!

00:03:28.099 --> 00:03:29.351
<i>Parsa.</i>

00:03:31.853 --> 00:03:32.604
Jared.

00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:36.024
Adwan.

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.403
Perez.

00:03:48.787 --> 00:03:49.955
Just one wrong.

00:03:49.955 --> 00:03:51.122
Congrats, Ms. Perez.

00:03:52.707 --> 00:03:53.875
Thank you!

00:03:58.797 --> 00:03:59.798
Yes!

00:04:03.843 --> 00:04:05.178
You look happy.

00:04:05.804 --> 00:04:07.973
Thanks for the paper you made, Tripp.

00:04:08.098 --> 00:04:08.932
Everything is in there.

00:04:09.516 --> 00:04:10.767
I got A plus.

00:04:11.559 --> 00:04:12.727
Anytime, Zy.

00:04:19.734 --> 00:04:21.319
It's almost time to go home.

00:04:23.905 --> 00:04:25.782
Just a quick reminder, everyone.

00:04:26.249 --> 00:04:30.370
Remember to read the History
of Advertising regarding identity...

00:04:30.921 --> 00:04:32.256
My love for you is crazy.

00:04:33.164 --> 00:04:34.666
And I don't like crazy.

00:04:35.539 --> 00:04:38.419
But being in love with you
makes me do crazy things.

00:04:38.878 --> 00:04:40.171
Makes me go to different heights,

00:04:40.171 --> 00:04:42.382
and to be honest,
it's scaring the shit out of me.

00:04:42.382 --> 00:04:44.509
But I love being in love with you Alys.

00:04:45.135 --> 00:04:46.428
And so long as I live,

00:04:46.666 --> 00:04:49.211
I'll continue loving you to
the moon and back, Alys.

00:04:49.523 --> 00:04:50.941
To the moon and back.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:53.868
Okay, everyone.

00:04:53.893 --> 00:04:55.395
I'll see you next week.

00:04:57.230 --> 00:04:58.106
Gotta go.

00:05:01.443 --> 00:05:02.902
Not even a goodbye?

00:07:04.623 --> 00:07:05.541
Drake!

00:07:07.001 --> 00:07:09.170
Wait. Are you leaving?

00:07:10.671 --> 00:07:11.881
<i>That's strange.</i>

00:07:11.881 --> 00:07:15.217
<i>Why does he feel like his old self?</i>
<i>The one who didn't care.</i>

00:07:15.217 --> 00:07:17.345
<i>You're overthinking this, Alys.</i>

00:07:17.345 --> 00:07:18.304
Drake!

00:07:18.304 --> 00:07:19.722
Are we going somewhere?

00:07:25.061 --> 00:07:26.103
Drake?

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:28.383
Are you leaving already?

00:07:28.564 --> 00:07:30.358
I thought you’ll stay
here for 7 days.

00:07:30.358 --> 00:07:32.052
It hasn't even been a week.

00:07:32.077 --> 00:07:33.165
Yes.

00:07:33.652 --> 00:07:34.570
I'm heading home.

00:07:35.352 --> 00:07:36.436
JFK Airport, sir.

00:07:36.461 --> 00:07:36.920
Yes, sir.

00:07:36.945 --> 00:07:38.572
Huh? Drake!

00:07:40.451 --> 00:07:41.535
Why, Drake?

00:07:42.078 --> 00:07:43.788
Did I do something wrong?

00:07:44.538 --> 00:07:46.374
Did I do something to hurt you?

00:07:49.752 --> 00:07:51.253
I'm not good for you, Alys.

00:07:58.969 --> 00:08:00.888
I won't lie to you since I hate lies.

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:03.474
Stop wasting your time on me.

00:08:03.933 --> 00:08:05.226
Stop thinking about me.

00:08:05.643 --> 00:08:06.852
You're here to study.

00:08:07.228 --> 00:08:09.230
Make your parents proud,
and make me proud.

00:08:09.772 --> 00:08:11.315
I'll study harder, Drake!

00:08:11.315 --> 00:08:13.275
You don't have to do this!

00:08:13.275 --> 00:08:14.360
- Please!
- Alys!

00:08:14.535 --> 00:08:15.945
Lower your voice.

00:08:17.446 --> 00:08:19.824
Promise, promise, Drake!
I'll study harder.

00:08:19.990 --> 00:08:21.867
Don't do this to me, Drake!

00:08:21.867 --> 00:08:23.577
Please don't leave me!

00:08:23.577 --> 00:08:25.079
I've made up my mind.

00:08:25.079 --> 00:08:26.539
Let's call it quits.

00:08:26.622 --> 00:08:28.999
Try and get in that cab, Drake!

00:08:30.209 --> 00:08:31.752
I'll forget I ever met you.

00:08:35.131 --> 00:08:36.924
I'll forget you even if it’s hard!

00:08:39.343 --> 00:08:41.679
Leave me now
and I promise you...

00:08:42.769 --> 00:08:44.854
I won't let you back in my life.

00:08:47.509 --> 00:08:48.927
I'll wait for you, Alys.

00:08:49.687 --> 00:08:51.313
Maybe we're not together now.

00:08:52.398 --> 00:08:54.108
But you'll always be my Alys.

00:08:54.108 --> 00:08:56.026
Drake, please don't leave me like this.

00:08:57.715 --> 00:08:58.924
I won't let you.

00:08:59.351 --> 00:09:01.198
I don't know what I'll do, Drake.

00:09:01.198 --> 00:09:02.616
Don’t you love me?

00:09:03.190 --> 00:09:05.233
Drake, don’t you love me anymore?

00:09:05.870 --> 00:09:06.912
Alys, study hard.

00:09:06.937 --> 00:09:08.022
Don't leave me!

00:09:08.047 --> 00:09:10.549
Go back to the Philippines and
make me regret letting you go.

00:09:10.916 --> 00:09:12.168
- Drake, Drake!
- Show me.

00:09:12.168 --> 00:09:13.586
I love you so much!

00:09:13.586 --> 00:09:15.309
Show me the fool that I am
for letting you go.

00:09:18.674 --> 00:09:21.218
Please, please, please!

00:09:24.961 --> 00:09:26.546
Drake!

00:09:27.933 --> 00:09:28.893
Drake!

00:09:29.268 --> 00:09:30.394
Drake!

00:09:33.606 --> 00:09:38.027
You will regret this, Drake Palma!

00:10:09.016 --> 00:10:09.975
Bestie...

00:10:11.352 --> 00:10:12.308
Don't cry.

00:10:14.712 --> 00:10:17.089
Maybe he had a reason
for leaving you.

00:10:17.314 --> 00:10:20.901
Whatever it is,
he could’ve told me, right?

00:10:21.403 --> 00:10:25.783
Why couldn't he just tell me?!

00:10:29.024 --> 00:10:30.901
Don't worry. I'll talk to him.

00:10:33.049 --> 00:10:34.759
Don't!
I don't want him thinking

00:10:34.833 --> 00:10:36.335
that I want him that badly.

00:10:36.360 --> 00:10:38.229
That I can't live without him!

00:10:38.254 --> 00:10:40.464
Why do you men
have to be like that?!

00:10:40.489 --> 00:10:41.156
What did I do?

00:10:41.507 --> 00:10:43.509
Does hurting us feel natural to you?

00:10:46.136 --> 00:10:47.221
You know what, Bestie?

00:10:47.718 --> 00:10:48.969
Let's get you something to eat.

00:10:49.306 --> 00:10:51.141
Even if I was the one who
visited you here.

00:10:51.642 --> 00:10:53.978
It's my treat. I promise!

00:10:56.355 --> 00:10:57.558
We're here for you.

00:11:01.235 --> 00:11:02.611
Let's enjoy ourselves.

00:11:02.611 --> 00:11:04.738
So you can let yourself
forget about Drake.

00:11:06.865 --> 00:11:08.284
What do you say?

00:11:11.537 --> 00:11:14.081
How could I forget him?

00:11:14.081 --> 00:11:14.832
Bestie!

00:11:15.457 --> 00:11:17.376
Alys! Alys!

00:11:17.376 --> 00:11:18.085
Bestie!

00:11:18.110 --> 00:11:18.861
Alys!

00:11:19.021 --> 00:11:20.523
- Bestie!
- Alys!

00:11:22.214 --> 00:11:23.632
- Bestie!
- Alys!

00:11:23.632 --> 00:11:26.093
We should have
arrived when Drake did.

00:11:27.052 --> 00:11:28.137
We could have skipped the tour.

00:11:28.762 --> 00:11:32.266
Didn't we agree to give
them two days on their own?

00:11:32.683 --> 00:11:34.810
I couldn't have known
this would happen.

00:11:35.603 --> 00:11:37.354
And, back off!

00:11:37.563 --> 00:11:39.356
You're the one who insisted
on doing the tour first

00:11:39.356 --> 00:11:42.460
because you're still gathering
the courage to see —

00:11:53.102 --> 00:11:54.345
Kei!

00:11:55.122 --> 00:11:56.464
Kei! Kei! Kei!

00:12:00.452 --> 00:12:02.252
Kei, you look amazing!

00:12:06.508 --> 00:12:08.802
Hey, it's your ex!

00:12:09.941 --> 00:12:12.235
He came all this way
just to see you, you know.

00:12:12.681 --> 00:12:13.974
Aya...

00:12:17.250 --> 00:12:18.459
Hi, Kei.

00:12:19.772 --> 00:12:20.565
Hi.

00:12:23.192 --> 00:12:25.069
You two.

00:12:28.530 --> 00:12:30.574
Oh! What happened?

00:12:30.901 --> 00:12:31.777
Nothing. Nevermind.

00:12:32.201 --> 00:12:33.702
Bestie! Bestie!

00:12:44.088 --> 00:12:45.276
Uhm...

00:12:46.367 --> 00:12:48.828
Why didn't you go eat with them?

00:12:51.306 --> 00:12:52.256
Why?

00:12:53.347 --> 00:12:54.509
Don’t you want me here?

00:12:57.831 --> 00:12:58.832
Uh...

00:12:59.724 --> 00:13:00.808
Not really.

00:13:02.970 --> 00:13:04.513
Maybe you miss your friend.

00:13:05.132 --> 00:13:07.050
Isn't that why you're here?

00:13:18.956 --> 00:13:20.196
Uh...

00:13:22.111 --> 00:13:23.611
You're still the Sheen I know.

00:13:26.839 --> 00:13:28.340
I'm still the Sheen you know.

00:13:29.466 --> 00:13:30.551
I haven't changed.

00:13:35.139 --> 00:13:36.181
Anyway...

00:13:37.099 --> 00:13:38.475
Long time no hear.

00:13:39.768 --> 00:13:41.637
I thought you went to Russia.

00:13:47.943 --> 00:13:48.736
Yeah.

00:13:49.319 --> 00:13:50.529
Change of plans.

00:13:55.121 --> 00:13:56.205
Well...

00:13:57.745 --> 00:13:59.496
looks like a lot has changed with you.

00:14:02.082 --> 00:14:03.834
You look good in blonde, by the way.

00:14:09.423 --> 00:14:10.429
Um...

00:14:12.707 --> 00:14:13.833
How long are you guys staying?

00:14:14.261 --> 00:14:15.235
Until tomorrow.

00:14:16.544 --> 00:14:17.563
Seems short.

00:14:18.182 --> 00:14:19.725
Classes are starting.

00:14:22.394 --> 00:14:23.520
Oh.

00:14:25.470 --> 00:14:26.596
Okay.

00:14:33.634 --> 00:14:34.593
Okay.

00:14:34.919 --> 00:14:36.046
I'll be going now.

00:14:36.829 --> 00:14:38.039
Uh, Sheen?

00:14:41.918 --> 00:14:43.086
Are you mad at me?

00:14:45.083 --> 00:14:45.959
Nope.

00:14:48.277 --> 00:14:49.221
Sure?

00:14:54.003 --> 00:14:55.838
Sorry for ghosting you.

00:14:58.138 --> 00:15:00.390
I just don't want you
holding back because of me.

00:15:06.104 --> 00:15:07.022
Don't worry.

00:15:08.106 --> 00:15:09.233
I understand.

00:15:13.469 --> 00:15:14.531
Friends?

00:15:14.965 --> 00:15:15.964
Friends.

00:15:17.313 --> 00:15:18.273
For now.

00:15:19.576 --> 00:15:20.452
Dinner?

00:15:20.869 --> 00:15:21.662
On me.

00:15:23.831 --> 00:15:24.915
You know?

00:15:26.333 --> 00:15:28.001
I really love you.

00:15:36.947 --> 00:15:38.156
I missed you.

00:15:40.097 --> 00:15:41.598
Across thousands of miles,

00:15:42.224 --> 00:15:44.101
my heart will always
be beside you.

00:15:47.240 --> 00:15:48.324
Same.

00:16:01.743 --> 00:16:04.121
I did everything I could, bestie.

00:16:08.709 --> 00:16:10.794
What else could I have done?

00:16:11.378 --> 00:16:13.297
I gave everything.

00:16:14.631 --> 00:16:15.507
Bestie...

00:16:16.550 --> 00:16:17.301
Don't cry.

00:16:18.802 --> 00:16:20.637
It hurts me to see you like this.

00:16:22.764 --> 00:16:25.517
If I ever see that Drake again...

00:16:26.268 --> 00:16:27.728
I'll punch him in the face!

00:16:28.854 --> 00:16:31.481
He can hurt anyone else.
Just not my best friend!

00:16:33.692 --> 00:16:35.527
I won't allow it!

00:16:39.597 --> 00:16:43.309
It's really hard to see you like this.

00:16:47.456 --> 00:16:49.541
I'm really glad you're here.

00:16:49.958 --> 00:16:51.418
Of course, bestie.

00:16:52.836 --> 00:16:55.380
At least I have someone to lean on.

00:17:00.010 --> 00:17:03.847
I'm sure that when you leave,
my world will fall apart again.

00:17:05.766 --> 00:17:08.638
I love you so much, bestie!

00:17:12.022 --> 00:17:13.751
I love you, besh.

00:17:15.067 --> 00:17:16.360
You can do this.

00:17:17.227 --> 00:17:18.812
I believe you will.

00:17:19.350 --> 00:17:22.155
You've been through
so much with Drake.

00:17:28.121 --> 00:17:30.165
Damn you, Drake Palma!

00:17:31.742 --> 00:17:34.870
You'll regret for leaving me, Drake!

00:17:50.012 --> 00:17:52.097
Drake, you're getting married!

00:17:56.147 --> 00:17:58.316
The marriage is not
until next month.

00:17:59.709 --> 00:18:00.321
So?

00:18:00.852 --> 00:18:01.978
What does that mean?

00:18:18.255 --> 00:18:20.007
I'm returning the favor, Alys.

00:18:20.465 --> 00:18:22.009
Tripp betrayed me.

00:18:22.132 --> 00:18:23.300
I'll do the same.

00:18:23.982 --> 00:18:25.191
See you around.

00:18:33.292 --> 00:18:35.377
<i>What are you doing, Drake?</i>

00:18:39.171 --> 00:18:42.004
I just don't understand why,
after all these years,

00:18:42.029 --> 00:18:43.739
he decides to come back.

00:18:43.739 --> 00:18:44.948
And in that way?

00:18:44.948 --> 00:18:46.825
It's just so toxic, right?

00:18:46.825 --> 00:18:47.743
Like —

00:18:47.743 --> 00:18:49.161
- Bestie...
- Bestie!

00:18:49.161 --> 00:18:50.996
- It's —
- Stop right there, Alys.

00:18:51.123 --> 00:18:52.279
You're making me dizzy.

00:18:52.581 --> 00:18:53.463
But —

00:18:54.037 --> 00:18:55.121
Bestie, come on.

00:18:55.654 --> 00:18:59.032
So you're telling me
that Drake's hit on you?

00:18:59.057 --> 00:19:00.188
Exactly!

00:19:00.213 --> 00:19:03.133
He's hit on me knowing
that he has a fiancé.

00:19:03.158 --> 00:19:05.702
He kissed me!
What a freakin' jerk!

00:19:05.890 --> 00:19:07.850
Poor Ms. Stinson.

00:19:08.269 --> 00:19:09.645
Maybe he's still into you.

00:19:11.058 --> 00:19:12.142
Still into me?

00:19:12.648 --> 00:19:13.690
Are you mad?

00:19:13.715 --> 00:19:14.883
Still into me?

00:19:14.908 --> 00:19:17.285
He's the one who left me, right?

00:19:17.781 --> 00:19:19.749
You were the only person who knew

00:19:19.775 --> 00:19:21.610
what I went through after he left me.

00:19:21.610 --> 00:19:25.065
Maybe seeing you again
brought back the old flame.

00:19:26.911 --> 00:19:28.287
Old flame my ass.

00:19:28.312 --> 00:19:29.313
I love Tripp!

00:19:29.338 --> 00:19:31.595
He’s the only one I loved.
Only him!

00:19:31.620 --> 00:19:33.831
Hey, I'm not saying anything, bestie.

00:19:34.087 --> 00:19:36.824
Maybe he thinks you're still into him.

00:19:38.200 --> 00:19:39.221
You know,

00:19:39.622 --> 00:19:42.542
what you guys had
was pretty great, okay?

00:19:43.607 --> 00:19:45.067
<i>I'll see you tomorrow!</i>

00:19:45.225 --> 00:19:47.185
Okay, I'll see you tomorrow.

00:19:47.844 --> 00:19:48.824
Okay!

00:20:06.988 --> 00:20:09.429
I've made up my mind.
Let's call it quits.

00:20:10.784 --> 00:20:12.691
Drake!

00:20:13.544 --> 00:20:16.547
Drake! Drake!

00:20:19.459 --> 00:20:22.671
You'll regret this, Drake Palma!

00:20:25.340 --> 00:20:26.476
Alright, fine!

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:27.848
It was great.

00:20:28.875 --> 00:20:31.669
But he put me through
a lot when he left, right?

00:20:31.763 --> 00:20:32.722
- It’s only great
- That’s right.

00:20:32.722 --> 00:20:34.975
in the sense if it was
the great depression.

00:20:34.975 --> 00:20:37.060
It's literally the worst!

00:20:38.776 --> 00:20:40.069
- Aya!
- Bestie.

00:20:40.264 --> 00:20:41.540
Calm down, bestie.

00:20:41.565 --> 00:20:42.774
Bestie, I've already been through this.

00:20:42.774 --> 00:20:44.818
- I'm not doing this again.
- I know! Please calm down!

00:20:44.843 --> 00:20:47.053
Bestie, would you settle down?

00:20:47.195 --> 00:20:50.574
- Aren't you done yet?
- Besh, I'm so sick and tired of this!

00:20:52.200 --> 00:20:53.410
My god!

00:20:55.472 --> 00:20:56.723
By the way, bestie,

00:20:57.873 --> 00:20:59.166
How are you and Kent?

00:20:59.708 --> 00:21:01.001
Still not talking, huh?

00:21:01.770 --> 00:21:02.687
Ouch!

00:21:03.904 --> 00:21:04.780
Sorry.

00:21:07.703 --> 00:21:09.831
That's what I've been saying.

00:21:10.594 --> 00:21:11.720
Come on, bestie.

00:21:11.928 --> 00:21:14.097
Kent and I broke up
only three months ago.

00:21:15.093 --> 00:21:16.764
It's too soon to talk.

00:21:17.615 --> 00:21:19.784
Bestie, nothing's too soon.

00:21:20.265 --> 00:21:20.933
You know,

00:21:20.958 --> 00:21:22.459
the more you don't talk to him,

00:21:22.533 --> 00:21:25.167
the more you'll forget the memories
you shared with him.

00:21:25.325 --> 00:21:27.368
And when you forget
those memories,

00:21:27.736 --> 00:21:29.821
moving on will just be a piece of cake.

00:21:31.091 --> 00:21:32.013
I agree.

00:21:34.691 --> 00:21:36.592
You’ll get pricked again.

00:21:38.163 --> 00:21:39.706
Are we doing real talk now, bestie?

00:21:39.731 --> 00:21:42.067
Bestie, don't be like that.
Don't change the subject.

00:21:42.626 --> 00:21:45.045
What I'm trying to say is,

00:21:45.458 --> 00:21:48.628
if you still love Kent,
which you obviously still do,

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:50.746
why not just talk to him?

00:21:51.051 --> 00:21:54.012
Before some skank snags him away.

00:21:55.222 --> 00:21:56.097
So?

00:21:56.097 --> 00:21:57.933
Are you gonna talk to him or not?

00:21:57.958 --> 00:21:59.502
To talk or not to talk?

00:22:00.518 --> 00:22:01.978
I'll think about it.

00:22:02.287 --> 00:22:05.757
The pain's all still a bit
too fresh on my mind, bestie.

00:22:12.072 --> 00:22:13.323
It's Ms. Stinson.

00:22:14.141 --> 00:22:16.685
<i>Hi, Alys, can we meet now?</i>

00:22:17.148 --> 00:22:19.662
But we just met earlier today.

00:22:20.337 --> 00:22:21.505
Okay.

00:22:21.983 --> 00:22:23.235
Bestie, I need to use the bathroom.

00:22:23.281 --> 00:22:24.193
Okay.

00:22:33.623 --> 00:22:34.983
Drake!

00:22:42.686 --> 00:22:43.728
Yuck!

00:22:43.885 --> 00:22:44.802
Alys!

00:22:45.146 --> 00:22:46.064
Alys!

00:22:46.485 --> 00:22:48.863
Did you really come all the way
to our apartment just to whine?

00:22:49.405 --> 00:22:50.781
It's been weeks!

00:22:53.137 --> 00:22:54.513
It’s so annoying!

00:22:55.813 --> 00:22:58.301
First, I couldn't finish my course work

00:22:58.326 --> 00:22:59.494
then Drake dumps me,

00:22:59.494 --> 00:23:01.955
and now I have to put up with you!

00:23:03.712 --> 00:23:05.297
Would you leave Zy alone, Tofer?!

00:23:06.293 --> 00:23:07.335
Fine, then!

00:23:07.919 --> 00:23:10.024
I'll listen to my music elsewhere.

00:23:12.470 --> 00:23:13.555
You're real loud.

00:23:13.580 --> 00:23:14.998
I couldn't hear anything.

00:23:15.389 --> 00:23:16.298
Good, finally.

00:23:18.709 --> 00:23:19.585
Crazy!

00:23:20.893 --> 00:23:22.353
Just go already!
Piss off, man!

00:23:23.063 --> 00:23:23.898
Unbelievable!

00:23:27.851 --> 00:23:28.796
Zy!

00:23:32.861 --> 00:23:34.404
Zy, are you sure you're alright?

00:23:36.878 --> 00:23:38.296
Your eyes are all red!

00:23:39.603 --> 00:23:40.688
Try to get some sleep.

00:23:43.383 --> 00:23:44.234
Zy...

00:23:47.500 --> 00:23:48.084
Hold on.

00:23:48.084 --> 00:23:49.085
I've got something for you, okay?

00:23:49.085 --> 00:23:49.878
Wait.

00:23:57.719 --> 00:23:58.803
Here.

00:23:59.554 --> 00:24:00.722
This is good.

00:24:01.261 --> 00:24:02.060
Here.

00:24:03.224 --> 00:24:04.351
It's really good, I promise.

00:24:09.898 --> 00:24:13.026
Damn it!
Even the ice cream won't cooperate!

00:24:18.531 --> 00:24:19.699
There, it's open!

00:24:20.002 --> 00:24:20.795
Sorry.

00:24:21.717 --> 00:24:24.011
Why is it all melted?!

00:24:24.496 --> 00:24:25.430
Wait!

00:24:25.455 --> 00:24:26.122
Wait!

00:24:26.456 --> 00:24:27.832
I forgot something!

00:24:34.419 --> 00:24:35.587
Here, Zy.

00:24:37.794 --> 00:24:38.962
Zy, eat up.

00:24:40.595 --> 00:24:43.098
It's really good Zy.
Taste it. There...

00:24:43.848 --> 00:24:44.974
Isn’t it good?

00:24:46.226 --> 00:24:47.352
Do you like it?

00:24:55.735 --> 00:24:57.404
Strawberry!

00:24:58.806 --> 00:24:59.932
But it's good.

00:25:04.857 --> 00:25:06.054
That’s all I've got Zy, sorry.

00:25:07.705 --> 00:25:08.790
Let me.

00:25:16.631 --> 00:25:17.316
Uh...

00:25:17.453 --> 00:25:18.579
I almost forgot Zy,

00:25:19.050 --> 00:25:20.848
I've got movie tickets.

00:25:21.655 --> 00:25:22.940
Want to go to the
Upper East Side later?

00:25:28.643 --> 00:25:29.618
Okay.

00:25:29.643 --> 00:25:30.519
Alright.

00:25:30.854 --> 00:25:31.900
You should eat first.

00:25:44.220 --> 00:25:45.346
Where are you going?

00:25:46.411 --> 00:25:48.079
It's really cold tonight.

00:25:48.529 --> 00:25:50.573
I might not just end up heartbroken,

00:25:51.758 --> 00:25:54.010
I might get brain freeze too.

00:25:55.952 --> 00:25:57.620
So where are you going, then?

00:25:58.940 --> 00:26:00.275
To the movies.

00:26:00.553 --> 00:26:01.887
Wanna come?

00:26:02.844 --> 00:26:03.595
Pass.

00:26:04.179 --> 00:26:05.388
Have a great time, though.

00:26:05.388 --> 00:26:06.389
You need it.

00:26:07.424 --> 00:26:08.258
Thanks, Kei.

00:26:08.762 --> 00:26:09.596
Bye, bye!

00:26:10.095 --> 00:26:11.013
Um, Alys!

00:26:12.457 --> 00:26:13.833
I wanted to ask you something.

00:26:19.730 --> 00:26:21.481
I don't want to be nosy, but...

00:26:22.005 --> 00:26:23.757
What's with you and Drake?

00:26:26.743 --> 00:26:27.708
Oh!

00:26:31.632 --> 00:26:32.925
We broke up.

00:26:36.366 --> 00:26:37.492
Oh.

00:26:38.171 --> 00:26:40.304
That was when Aya was here.

00:26:41.225 --> 00:26:43.311
I saw you crying then denied it after.

00:26:45.720 --> 00:26:47.472
Yes, that’s right.

00:26:50.350 --> 00:26:51.476
Come, Alys.

00:26:52.685 --> 00:26:54.312
Sit here for a moment.

00:27:04.155 --> 00:27:05.156
What's up?

00:27:08.991 --> 00:27:10.285
Everything will be fine.

00:27:11.538 --> 00:27:12.553
He's a jackass.

00:27:12.730 --> 00:27:13.981
For letting you go.

00:27:15.760 --> 00:27:16.761
You'll be fine.

00:27:17.372 --> 00:27:18.373
Promise.

00:27:20.579 --> 00:27:21.580
Thanks, Kei.

00:27:23.338 --> 00:27:24.840
So, if you need a friend,

00:27:25.784 --> 00:27:26.785
I'm just here.

00:27:27.718 --> 00:27:28.886
It’s just the two of us here.

00:27:29.596 --> 00:27:31.390
We should look out for each other.

00:27:36.813 --> 00:27:37.855
Thanks, Kei.

00:27:38.969 --> 00:27:40.637
I really appreciate it.

00:27:43.046 --> 00:27:44.089
Weren't you going somewhere?

00:27:44.753 --> 00:27:45.796
Oh yeah, I was.

00:27:46.226 --> 00:27:47.686
Don't be late for your movie.

00:27:48.887 --> 00:27:49.596
Go!

00:27:50.826 --> 00:27:51.535
Okay.

00:27:51.995 --> 00:27:52.887
Bye!

00:27:53.413 --> 00:27:54.305
Thanks, Kei.

00:27:54.529 --> 00:27:55.404
Bye!

00:27:57.614 --> 00:27:58.378
Enjoy!

00:27:59.002 --> 00:27:59.885
Thank you!

00:28:04.674 --> 00:28:06.551
That movie was funny.

00:28:07.343 --> 00:28:08.386
What do you think?

00:28:09.379 --> 00:28:10.505
I didn't find it funny.

00:28:10.990 --> 00:28:11.894
What?!

00:28:12.015 --> 00:28:13.224
You didn't laugh?

00:28:13.224 --> 00:28:14.434
Not even at the penguin?

00:28:14.434 --> 00:28:15.643
It was like...

00:28:20.565 --> 00:28:22.564
- I mean, I did laugh but...
- There you go again.

00:28:22.589 --> 00:28:23.674
You’re messing with me again.

00:28:24.115 --> 00:28:26.242
It’s just cold, I feel sleepy.

00:28:26.696 --> 00:28:29.907
I don't get why it's so cold.
It's not even winter yet.

00:28:40.293 --> 00:28:41.419
Hey!

00:28:42.420 --> 00:28:43.546
Hey!

00:28:44.005 --> 00:28:45.131
Tripp...

00:28:45.673 --> 00:28:46.799
It's all good, Zyril.

00:28:47.191 --> 00:28:48.457
No malice here.

00:28:49.071 --> 00:28:50.443
I just don't want you to get cold.

00:29:06.213 --> 00:29:08.423
<i>His hands are so warm.</i>

00:29:08.738 --> 00:29:10.657
<i>Drake's hands were so cold.</i>

00:29:11.240 --> 00:29:12.311
<i>Come on, Alys!</i>

00:29:12.506 --> 00:29:14.090
<i>Stop comparing!</i>

00:29:18.956 --> 00:29:20.166
Better?

00:29:20.541 --> 00:29:21.321
Thanks!

00:29:23.253 --> 00:29:24.880
No, don't mention it.

00:29:25.213 --> 00:29:25.966
Of course!

00:29:26.798 --> 00:29:27.607
Come on.

00:29:27.632 --> 00:29:28.459
Let's get sushi.

00:29:29.425 --> 00:29:30.193
Okay!

00:29:30.218 --> 00:29:31.214
As long as it’s your treat!

00:29:31.994 --> 00:29:33.787
- Treat again?
- On you, Tripp!

00:29:37.392 --> 00:29:38.851
Okay, Dane!

00:29:38.851 --> 00:29:40.269
Come on, let's eat!

00:29:42.647 --> 00:29:44.268
- Alys!
- Surprise!

00:29:45.831 --> 00:29:47.582
Mommy!

00:29:47.694 --> 00:29:49.028
Oh, my god. I missed you!

00:29:49.620 --> 00:29:50.955
Dad!

00:29:50.988 --> 00:29:52.740
- Why are you here? I mean...
- I miss you so much!

00:29:53.199 --> 00:29:55.037
We're happy you're here, but...

00:29:55.062 --> 00:29:56.035
Why are you here?!

00:29:56.035 --> 00:29:56.869
Actually,

00:29:56.869 --> 00:29:57.829
my plane landed a while ago.

00:29:57.829 --> 00:29:59.722
I just went to see Aya for a bit.

00:29:59.747 --> 00:30:02.815
Well before that, I also went
to my shop to meet with a client.

00:30:02.840 --> 00:30:04.425
So...here I am!

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:05.796
Shop?

00:30:06.129 --> 00:30:06.671
Yes, Dad.

00:30:06.671 --> 00:30:08.923
I've been working on it secretly,

00:30:08.923 --> 00:30:12.717
but I'm finally opening my
own cupcake shop business!

00:30:13.261 --> 00:30:15.012
I'm staying here for good!

00:30:15.054 --> 00:30:16.139
That’s good!

00:30:17.793 --> 00:30:19.826
Wait, oh my gosh!
I love what you did to the place!

00:30:19.851 --> 00:30:21.160
Is this you, mom?

00:30:21.185 --> 00:30:22.311
Of course!

00:30:22.311 --> 00:30:23.646
So pretty!

00:30:24.942 --> 00:30:26.657
Baby Dane!

00:30:27.400 --> 00:30:28.943
You're here! Oh my gosh!

00:30:28.943 --> 00:30:31.404
I missed you!
But I also got you something!

00:30:31.404 --> 00:30:33.114
I'll show you! Come!

00:30:34.490 --> 00:30:35.700
For mom,

00:30:35.700 --> 00:30:38.286
of course, I got you jewelry!

00:30:38.286 --> 00:30:40.163
Yes! Thank you, baby!

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:42.373
For Dad, your favorite perfume.

00:30:42.541 --> 00:30:43.666
Thank you, thank you.

00:30:43.832 --> 00:30:46.294
And of course, for my Baby Dane,

00:30:46.294 --> 00:30:47.754
the books that I promised!

00:30:47.754 --> 00:30:48.963
Yo!

00:30:49.036 --> 00:30:49.917
Thanks!

00:30:50.631 --> 00:30:52.717
As long as you stay a good boy!

00:30:53.505 --> 00:30:55.590
Alys, are you sure about your plan?

00:30:56.243 --> 00:30:57.286
Yes, Dad.

00:30:57.311 --> 00:30:58.354
I'm sure.

00:30:58.973 --> 00:31:00.016
What did Tripp say?

00:31:01.142 --> 00:31:03.478
<i>Took us almost three years</i>
<i>before we had the guts</i>

00:31:03.478 --> 00:31:05.813
<i>to admit that we want to be together.</i>

00:31:06.439 --> 00:31:07.446
He's okay with it.

00:31:07.471 --> 00:31:08.742
He plans to come join me.

00:31:08.767 --> 00:31:10.435
He’s just wrapping things up in New York.

00:31:10.610 --> 00:31:12.528
Okay, uhm... Wait a minute!

00:31:12.667 --> 00:31:13.877
What about this client?

00:31:13.988 --> 00:31:15.448
Yes, this client.

00:31:15.448 --> 00:31:17.909
Okay, before we talk about it,
let's eat first okay?

00:31:17.909 --> 00:31:18.618
Come on, come on.

00:31:18.643 --> 00:31:20.102
Perfect, I'm starving!

00:31:21.743 --> 00:31:24.037
And I love your shop, Mom!

00:31:24.165 --> 00:31:25.208
Thanks, dear!

00:31:27.826 --> 00:31:29.077
Did you miss us?

00:31:29.212 --> 00:31:30.641
I missed you so much.

00:31:31.069 --> 00:31:32.356
Okay! Let's eat.

00:31:32.381 --> 00:31:33.261
Help yourself.

00:31:33.466 --> 00:31:34.300
Yehey!

00:31:34.416 --> 00:31:35.162
Let's eat.

00:32:03.253 --> 00:32:06.256
Do we really have to
meet here of all places?

00:32:27.397 --> 00:32:28.690
Good evening.

00:32:28.715 --> 00:32:29.757
Dinner?

00:32:33.776 --> 00:32:34.819
Is it just you?

00:32:35.111 --> 00:32:36.473
Where's Ms. Stinson?

00:32:36.612 --> 00:32:38.072
I thought she called to meet me

00:32:38.072 --> 00:32:39.532
so she could choose a cake?

00:32:39.996 --> 00:32:41.456
Alys, dinner?

00:32:43.995 --> 00:32:44.912
I'll call her.

00:32:44.912 --> 00:32:46.539
If she'll not be here,
I'm leaving.

00:33:13.982 --> 00:33:15.400
Why is her phone with you?

00:33:16.819 --> 00:33:18.237
She left it with me.

00:33:18.796 --> 00:33:21.090
Because that's how relationships work.

00:33:21.115 --> 00:33:22.783
You need to trust your partner.

00:33:25.328 --> 00:33:26.245
Waiter!

00:33:29.081 --> 00:33:29.599
Yes, Ma’am?

00:33:29.624 --> 00:33:31.042
I'd like to place an order.

00:33:31.250 --> 00:33:34.670
Give me your most expensive
meat dish on the menu.

00:33:35.226 --> 00:33:36.201
Whatever it is.

00:33:38.215 --> 00:33:39.300
Okay, Ma’am.

00:33:42.678 --> 00:33:43.888
Okay, sure.

00:33:44.138 --> 00:33:45.973
You want to talk about trust?

00:33:46.098 --> 00:33:47.475
Want to do it now?

00:33:48.789 --> 00:33:50.165
We'll have time for that.

00:33:51.017 --> 00:33:52.144
But for now,

00:33:52.696 --> 00:33:54.281
what's with the skimpy attire?

00:33:56.233 --> 00:33:57.276
Pardon me?

00:33:58.639 --> 00:34:00.851
Really short shorts – check!

00:34:01.155 --> 00:34:03.824
Extra thin top – check!

00:34:04.575 --> 00:34:06.619
I can see your lace bra from here.

00:34:10.539 --> 00:34:12.802
Black stilettos – check!

00:34:13.209 --> 00:34:17.472
And very distracting red lipstick – check!

00:34:17.797 --> 00:34:19.215
Very skimpy attire.

00:34:22.859 --> 00:34:24.804
For your information, Drake.

00:34:24.804 --> 00:34:27.556
This is what we call a fashion trend.

00:34:27.749 --> 00:34:29.001
Ever heard of it?

00:34:29.364 --> 00:34:30.286
Sure.

00:34:30.595 --> 00:34:32.347
Does Tripp like it that way?

00:34:34.647 --> 00:34:36.273
Tripp likes me

00:34:36.273 --> 00:34:38.779
in every and any way.

00:34:45.053 --> 00:34:46.513
Good for him.

00:34:47.493 --> 00:34:48.369
Thanks.

00:34:48.501 --> 00:34:50.044
I don't like you that way.

00:34:51.101 --> 00:34:52.556
I'm gonna date you tonight.

00:34:52.581 --> 00:34:53.541
Go change.

00:35:01.590 --> 00:35:03.634
I hate it! I hate it so much.

00:35:13.185 --> 00:35:14.433
That's enough, Zy.

00:35:17.732 --> 00:35:19.233
You're just abusing yourself.

00:35:20.657 --> 00:35:22.367
You and Drake just broke up.

00:35:22.835 --> 00:35:24.128
He didn't die.

00:35:26.949 --> 00:35:28.868
But I still love him.

00:35:36.748 --> 00:35:37.582
I know.

00:35:38.419 --> 00:35:39.253
But,

00:35:39.955 --> 00:35:42.082
the world doesn't stop turning, Zy.

00:35:42.576 --> 00:35:43.502
Okay?

00:35:44.453 --> 00:35:45.621
Maybe

00:35:46.110 --> 00:35:48.279
Drake had a reason for doing that.

00:35:48.483 --> 00:35:49.525
But,

00:35:49.972 --> 00:35:51.015
despite of it,

00:35:51.766 --> 00:35:53.434
you have to take care of yourself.

00:35:56.228 --> 00:35:57.646
You're still young.

00:35:58.486 --> 00:35:59.904
You're still going to meet
a lot of people.

00:36:06.906 --> 00:36:08.939
But I don't want anyone else.

00:36:11.243 --> 00:36:13.412
Drake is the one I like.

00:36:23.214 --> 00:36:24.656
Believe me, I know.

00:36:25.800 --> 00:36:27.635
What was the last thing he
said before you broke up?

00:36:34.920 --> 00:36:36.400
"Make me proud."

00:36:38.832 --> 00:36:39.708
There it is, then!

00:36:41.440 --> 00:36:42.396
So how's it going?

00:36:44.985 --> 00:36:47.446
It's not as easy as it sounds, Tripp.

00:36:47.880 --> 00:36:50.216
It's not like in the movies where

00:36:50.241 --> 00:36:53.994
the girl gets hurt then magically
becomes prettier or smarter.

00:36:54.190 --> 00:36:55.579
Or braver.

00:36:55.865 --> 00:36:57.629
That's not real life.

00:36:58.999 --> 00:37:00.459
Just because he left me,

00:37:00.459 --> 00:37:03.087
it doesn't mean I'm suddenly
going to grow brain cells, right?

00:37:06.969 --> 00:37:08.165
You know what?
Let's go out.

00:37:08.978 --> 00:37:10.104
Come on!

00:37:10.501 --> 00:37:11.627
Let's go somewhere.

00:37:12.197 --> 00:37:13.031
You coming?

00:37:17.434 --> 00:37:18.384
What do you say?

00:37:26.527 --> 00:37:27.862
It's so good!

00:37:28.654 --> 00:37:30.297
Thank you so much, Tripp!

00:37:30.322 --> 00:37:32.408
I haven't eaten like this in a while.

00:37:33.068 --> 00:37:35.154
Whoever told you to stop eating?

00:37:40.103 --> 00:37:41.813
I want another bagel.

00:37:42.251 --> 00:37:43.085
Huh?

00:37:43.752 --> 00:37:45.248
- The bagel vendor is not here.
- There’s none left.

00:37:46.172 --> 00:37:47.423
The bagel vendor is not here.

00:37:47.882 --> 00:37:50.050
I want another bagel!

00:37:50.420 --> 00:37:51.552
But he's gone!

00:37:51.711 --> 00:37:53.379
But I want another one!

00:37:53.804 --> 00:37:55.306
I want another bagel!

00:37:55.681 --> 00:37:56.949
What do you want me to do?

00:37:56.974 --> 00:37:58.642
Make me a bagel!

00:37:59.935 --> 00:38:01.145
- Tripp!
- Whatever.

00:38:01.145 --> 00:38:03.439
Make me a bagel, please?

00:38:06.483 --> 00:38:08.027
Wow!

00:38:09.069 --> 00:38:10.946
Good thing Tofer's not around.

00:38:10.946 --> 00:38:12.156
I get these all for myself.

00:38:12.181 --> 00:38:13.474
And I can eat without that bully.

00:38:13.949 --> 00:38:14.617
Jeez,

00:38:14.722 --> 00:38:15.848
you're both bullies.

00:38:16.994 --> 00:38:18.287
Whatever.

00:38:18.287 --> 00:38:19.163
You know what?

00:38:19.163 --> 00:38:21.415
I was teasing him yesterday,
then he kissed me on the cheek.

00:38:21.415 --> 00:38:22.958
That ugly one is such a pain.

00:38:24.418 --> 00:38:25.794
It's my first time
making these, okay?

00:38:27.630 --> 00:38:29.381
So don't complain if
they don't taste good.

00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:32.051
Well, I'm hungry so
I'll eat anything.

00:38:32.635 --> 00:38:34.570
Hey! That's mean.

00:38:34.595 --> 00:38:36.388
It's like you're saying
I'm not good at it.

00:38:36.764 --> 00:38:37.806
You’re not good at it?

00:38:37.932 --> 00:38:39.099
Okay, fine.

00:38:39.767 --> 00:38:40.935
You're cute.

00:38:41.477 --> 00:38:42.478
All good?

00:38:43.520 --> 00:38:44.813
Go ahead and take a seat.

00:38:44.892 --> 00:38:45.893
- Okay.
- I'll just finish up.

00:38:46.023 --> 00:38:46.996
Thank you.

00:39:09.730 --> 00:39:10.731
Stalker!

00:39:10.935 --> 00:39:12.562
Why do I have a picture here?

00:39:26.815 --> 00:39:30.443
Tripp Marco is seriously crushing on me.

00:39:51.964 --> 00:39:53.316
He has Drake's number!

00:39:56.510 --> 00:39:57.915
Should I text him?

00:40:02.057 --> 00:40:04.059
<i>Don't, Alys!</i>

00:40:04.059 --> 00:40:06.645
<i>You've texted him enough already.</i>

00:40:06.645 --> 00:40:08.939
<i>He never replies.</i>

00:40:08.939 --> 00:40:10.482
<i>Enough already, please?</i>

00:40:13.444 --> 00:40:15.237
Who are you kidding, Alys?

00:40:18.699 --> 00:40:21.827
<i>Aren't you...</i>

00:40:22.126 --> 00:40:24.462
<i>going to ask... Alys?</i>

00:40:28.401 --> 00:40:30.195
I'm almost done here, alright?

00:40:31.122 --> 00:40:33.208
Oh! Okay!

00:40:33.233 --> 00:40:34.609
I'm starving!

00:41:42.104 --> 00:41:44.649
So you really don't love me anymore?

00:41:47.246 --> 00:41:48.789
Okay, Zy. It’s ready.

00:41:49.552 --> 00:41:50.707
Come on, let’s eat.

00:41:51.708 --> 00:41:52.601
Let’s go.

00:41:52.626 --> 00:41:53.836
This is a lot.

00:41:54.336 --> 00:41:55.671
It’s basic to make —

00:41:56.296 --> 00:41:57.214
Hey!

00:41:57.873 --> 00:41:58.749
Are you okay?

00:41:59.133 --> 00:42:00.217
You're crying again!

00:42:00.456 --> 00:42:02.124
My tummy's aching.

00:42:02.535 --> 00:42:03.494
Huh?

00:42:03.519 --> 00:42:04.366
Are you sure?

00:42:05.324 --> 00:42:06.576
Are you sure? Here. Come on.

00:42:06.932 --> 00:42:08.100
Come on, eat.

00:42:09.564 --> 00:42:10.624
There's a lot.

00:42:13.489 --> 00:42:14.706
- They're all yours.
- Ahh!

00:42:14.731 --> 00:42:15.399
Ouch.

00:42:15.512 --> 00:42:16.471
They're really hot.

00:42:16.867 --> 00:42:17.951
- Sorry.
- You didn't tell me.

00:42:17.995 --> 00:42:18.746
Hold on.

00:42:26.459 --> 00:42:27.261
Here.

00:42:28.268 --> 00:42:29.477
Put some toothpaste on it.

00:42:30.389 --> 00:42:32.349
What do I do with that?
Brush my teeth?

00:42:33.176 --> 00:42:34.010
You're crazy.

00:42:34.495 --> 00:42:35.371
Where does it hurt?

00:42:37.618 --> 00:42:38.411
Let’s put some on.

00:42:38.673 --> 00:42:39.544
Here?

00:42:39.882 --> 00:42:40.813
Here?

00:42:41.915 --> 00:42:42.726
Where?

00:42:44.136 --> 00:42:44.978
Here.

00:43:43.259 --> 00:43:44.338
That should be fine.

00:43:44.755 --> 00:43:46.882
Just give it a few minutes.

00:43:46.907 --> 00:43:48.575
Uhm...It'll heal.

00:43:51.370 --> 00:43:53.664
Don't take this the wrong way, Tripp.

00:43:55.358 --> 00:43:57.099
Have you had your first kiss?

00:44:01.588 --> 00:44:02.673
You don’t need to answer.

00:44:02.673 --> 00:44:04.299
I’ll just get some water.

00:44:08.679 --> 00:44:09.596
<i>Tripp...</i>

00:44:09.972 --> 00:44:11.139
<i>No.</i>

00:44:13.101 --> 00:44:14.113
First kiss?

00:44:16.223 --> 00:44:17.391
No, I don’t have.

00:44:18.843 --> 00:44:20.748
I've just been waiting for the girl

00:44:20.863 --> 00:44:22.991
who'll make my heart beat.

00:44:24.264 --> 00:44:26.558
Corny as it may be, but...

00:44:27.715 --> 00:44:28.966
it's the truth.

00:44:30.367 --> 00:44:32.578
The girl I love, well,

00:44:33.146 --> 00:44:34.135
she loves someone else.

00:44:37.181 --> 00:44:38.641
All I can hope for is

00:44:39.544 --> 00:44:41.879
that she'll forget about
my jerk cousin.

00:44:43.820 --> 00:44:45.229
So, she'll notice me.

00:44:47.634 --> 00:44:49.136
And she’ll finally realize

00:44:49.850 --> 00:44:51.852
that there’s one Tripp Marco Palma

00:44:52.505 --> 00:44:53.964
who loves her.

00:44:57.519 --> 00:44:59.062
What are you doing?!

00:44:59.271 --> 00:45:00.981
Why are you hugging each other?!

00:45:01.481 --> 00:45:02.399
Porn!

00:45:02.399 --> 00:45:04.067
- I'm telling Uncle!
- Calm down, Tofer!

00:45:04.067 --> 00:45:04.985
Alys!

00:45:04.985 --> 00:45:06.304
Don't even deny it!

00:45:06.329 --> 00:45:09.239
I just saw you with
my own tantalizing eyes!

00:45:09.239 --> 00:45:10.521
I'm telling Uncle!

00:45:10.546 --> 00:45:11.839
I'm telling on you!

00:45:18.790 --> 00:45:21.043
Let’s toast to our reunion date —

00:45:21.272 --> 00:45:22.857
after so long.

00:45:25.005 --> 00:45:26.340
Are you nuts?!

00:45:26.673 --> 00:45:28.759
Seriously, Drake,
what is wrong with you?

00:45:29.236 --> 00:45:30.993
Nothing is wrong with me, Alys?

00:45:31.018 --> 00:45:32.978
Then why are you doing this?!

00:45:33.333 --> 00:45:34.585
Why am I doing what?

00:45:44.092 --> 00:45:46.136
You're playing with me.
Damn, Drake!

00:45:47.483 --> 00:45:48.985
We're done with each other!

00:45:49.298 --> 00:45:52.426
Four years and counting.
And now you're back with this?!

00:45:53.033 --> 00:45:55.661
I thought you made it clear
that you didn't want me?

00:45:56.828 --> 00:45:57.913
I am done!

00:45:58.246 --> 00:45:59.119
Okay?

00:45:59.206 --> 00:46:00.916
So, please...

00:46:01.022 --> 00:46:03.441
Spare me from your emotional torture.

00:46:06.107 --> 00:46:08.067
<i>God, I'm losing my cool!</i>

00:46:08.632 --> 00:46:10.175
<i>Where the hell is Tripp?</i>

00:46:11.551 --> 00:46:13.011
<i>Don't worry, Zyril.</i>

00:46:13.011 --> 00:46:15.472
<i>Your boyfriend will</i>
<i>be here in three days.</i>

00:46:16.139 --> 00:46:17.432
<i>Hold on.</i>

00:46:22.228 --> 00:46:24.438
There's no emotional torture here, Alys.

00:46:25.496 --> 00:46:27.039
I'm just dating you tonight.

00:46:27.064 --> 00:46:28.691
What's so wrong with that?

00:46:32.337 --> 00:46:34.883
<i>Back then, I was naive and gullible.</i>

00:46:34.908 --> 00:46:35.992
<i>But now?</i>

00:46:35.992 --> 00:46:37.869
<i>I'm a whole lot better</i>
<i>and I won't give him</i>

00:46:37.869 --> 00:46:39.663
<i>the liberty to toy with me again.</i>

00:46:41.720 --> 00:46:43.513
Where do you think you're going?

00:46:43.980 --> 00:46:44.689
Home.

00:46:45.410 --> 00:46:46.369
I'm tired, okay?

00:46:47.295 --> 00:46:48.588
I haven't slept.

00:46:49.214 --> 00:46:52.540
And I'm about to lose my freakin' sanity.

00:46:52.969 --> 00:46:55.555
So please, don't make things any harder.

00:46:56.185 --> 00:46:57.520
Seriously, Drake!

00:46:58.395 --> 00:47:00.147
I don't want you back!

00:47:00.387 --> 00:47:03.562
So please, stop bothering me!

00:47:12.292 --> 00:47:14.325
<i>You're evil!</i>

00:47:14.592 --> 00:47:16.908
You're so unfair, Drake!

00:47:19.632 --> 00:47:21.133
What if,

00:47:22.007 --> 00:47:23.429
I've already fallen for you?

00:47:23.454 --> 00:47:24.997
It changes nothing?

00:47:25.850 --> 00:47:26.767
I lose everything

00:47:26.792 --> 00:47:28.753
because you don't love me!

00:47:29.599 --> 00:47:31.559
<i>I'm so tired.</i>

00:47:32.340 --> 00:47:33.550
If you don't want me,

00:47:33.550 --> 00:47:35.444
won't you just tell me?

00:47:35.782 --> 00:47:38.159
<i>Don't make me look like a fool.</i>

00:47:38.500 --> 00:47:39.639
You're too late.

00:47:39.899 --> 00:47:41.818
You're way too late.

00:47:43.472 --> 00:47:44.709
Do you know why?

00:47:46.813 --> 00:47:49.149
Because you've hurt me too much.

00:47:50.597 --> 00:47:53.308
<i>It's too late for me to forgive you.</i>

00:48:21.765 --> 00:48:22.974
I’ve made up my mind.

00:48:22.974 --> 00:48:24.304
Let's call it quits.

00:48:25.560 --> 00:48:28.146
Try and get in that cab, Drake!

00:48:29.189 --> 00:48:30.524
I will forget you.

00:48:33.735 --> 00:48:35.862
I'll forget you even if it’s hard!

00:48:36.822 --> 00:48:39.241
Leave me now
and I promise you...

00:48:40.116 --> 00:48:42.494
I won't let you back in my life.

00:48:43.203 --> 00:48:44.496
I'll wait for you, Alys.

00:48:45.664 --> 00:48:47.374
Maybe, we're not together now.

00:48:48.625 --> 00:48:50.542
- But you'll always be my Alys.
- Drake, please.

00:48:50.567 --> 00:48:52.861
Drake, please don't leave me like this.

00:48:54.089 --> 00:48:55.757
I won't let you.

00:48:55.757 --> 00:48:57.425
I don't know what I'll do, Drake.

00:48:57.425 --> 00:48:59.177
Don’t you love me anymore?

00:48:59.684 --> 00:49:00.852
Study hard.

00:49:01.142 --> 00:49:03.937
Go back to the Philippines and
make me regret letting you go.

00:49:05.362 --> 00:49:06.488
Show me.

00:49:06.746 --> 00:49:08.081
Show me the fool that I am

00:49:08.798 --> 00:49:10.049
for breaking up with you.

00:49:10.219 --> 00:49:11.521
Don't you love me?

00:49:15.595 --> 00:49:16.972
Please, please!

00:49:21.408 --> 00:49:22.492
Drake!

00:49:24.286 --> 00:49:28.415
<i>You will regret this, Drake Palma!</i>

00:49:33.295 --> 00:49:34.963
<i>I’m sorry, Alys.</i>

00:49:37.632 --> 00:49:38.800
<i>I’m sorry.</i>

00:49:40.444 --> 00:49:42.029
<i>This is for you, Alys.</i>

00:49:43.054 --> 00:49:44.854
<i>I will do this for you.</i>

00:49:49.350 --> 00:49:51.060
<i>Because I’m destroying you.</i>

00:49:52.685 --> 00:49:55.437
<i>You'll only be more devastated if I stay.</i>

00:49:59.613 --> 00:50:02.282
<i>When all of this is over, </i>
<i>I'll come back to you.</i>

00:50:11.041 --> 00:50:13.293
<i>I’ll find my way back to you.</i>

00:50:13.668 --> 00:50:16.046
<i>And I'll make sure </i>
<i>we still end up together.</i>

00:50:34.105 --> 00:50:36.149
<i>Wherever life takes me,</i>

00:50:37.525 --> 00:50:39.778
<i>I will always love you, Alys.</i>

00:50:44.273 --> 00:50:45.406
<i>[In French] Only you.</i>

00:51:09.349 --> 00:51:12.702
<i>On the next episode of </i>
<i>Dating Alys Perez.</i>

00:51:12.727 --> 00:51:14.562
How're wedding preparations going?

00:51:14.562 --> 00:51:16.231
Kinda stressful.

00:51:16.231 --> 00:51:18.650
Good thing Drake's really
hands on with all this stuff.

00:51:18.650 --> 00:51:20.402
One in a million, that he is.

00:51:20.568 --> 00:51:22.487
What's really going on
between you and Alys?

00:51:22.487 --> 00:51:23.780
You love Alys,

00:51:24.030 --> 00:51:24.882
don't you?

00:51:25.115 --> 00:51:25.922
So much.

00:51:27.492 --> 00:51:28.034
Quit it.

00:51:28.034 --> 00:51:29.035
You don't need me, anyway.

00:51:29.035 --> 00:51:30.053
You need Drake.

00:51:30.078 --> 00:51:31.796
What do you mean I need Drake?

00:51:35.125 --> 00:51:36.142
Where are we going?

00:51:36.167 --> 00:51:37.460
What do you mean
where are we going?

00:51:37.460 --> 00:51:38.586
Why are you even here?

00:51:38.586 --> 00:51:39.521
Feeling close?

00:51:39.546 --> 00:51:40.549
Are we close now?

00:51:40.594 --> 00:51:41.402
Alys,

00:51:41.798 --> 00:51:42.966
we were pretty close.

00:51:43.717 --> 00:51:44.884
We're exes, right?

00:51:44.884 --> 00:51:45.884
